    "body": "I suggest making \"remove\" safer by blocking requests to remove the last account.\r\nFor making it possible to remove all roles (which is sometimes desirable) there are a few options:\r\n1. Adding a new function \"removeLast\". So it won't happen by accident.\r\n2. Leaving it as-is and let the users find a way to achieve that functionality. For example add Role to a non-upgradable contract address that does not have the capability to call the relevant current contract functions.",
