    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "While interesting, there are many situations when it is contracts that have the role, and adding this would mean that they'd have to do a sort of try/catch attempt, calling `removeLast` if the first call fails, which makes the whole thing superfluous. Additionally, this would require `Roles` being aware of how many accounts have the role, and it currently lacks this capability (see #1602).",
